If you use this, give me some credit, or atleast PM me :P i would like to see what you make out of my server :P
some commands ::Skilling ::train (2,3) ::starter This is my first server source, please lighten up on me :P
HOME AND SHTUFF [IMG]http://i282.photobucket.com/albums/kk269/xxpk3rxxr/server10.jpg[/img]
ITEM TRAINING ZONE [IMG]http://i282.photobucket.com/albums/kk269/xxpk3rxxr/server20.jpg[/img]
ITEM TRAINING CONTINUED... [IMG]http://i282.photobucket.com/albums/kk269/xxpk3rxxr/server30.jpg[/img]
COMBAT AND TABS... [IMG]http://i282.photobucket.com/albums/kk269/xxpk3rxxr/afinal-1.jpg[/img]
Almost forgot virus scan :P [IMG]http://i282.photobucket.com/albums/kk269/xxpk3rxxr/abscan.jpg[/img]
Some things that arn't in pictures: same training ( ::train, ::train2, and ::train3 ) Turned guthans mini into a h'ween event Removed ::master and ::pure, turned into ::skiller some skills (thieving and the range target) train really fast, you can change it skilling zone is completly new (atleast to me) all skills can be found there besides mage and RC. (use ::rc and ::runes) old shops are at ::shops, but some shops have been moved to home. I added a cool starting outfit :P (lunar armor, cav. mask, ect.)
DL link: http://uppit.com/YG0EAV **FIXED** i need to see how i've done, if you think i did good, say so, if i need to fix something, i will fix in V2 so please post! :)
Thanks, Skye.
Add my AIM to chat and stuff :P Xx1 pk3r 1xX
Edit: the reason why everything is put into one place is because the wild zones are everywhere... i was lucky to find this
